{"tid":319311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人發覺韓國既健身風氣好流行","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T09:25:46.000Z","uid":98680,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f850dc8eb5f05c1f8ee49b212ec638770136883","tid":319311,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"而加睇ig好多韓國既men physical <br />\n而且身高都有返咁上下 平均都6尺以上<br />\n但多數隻腳都好撚幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/003303_e7c4337996ed3e93b1014eb48f64245d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F003303_e7c4337996ed3e93b1014eb48f64245d.jpg&h=c7e60f13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/003304_3a5bb20992696b5a0375e532973a401a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F003304_3a5bb20992696b5a0375e532973a401a.jpg&h=0d1a6002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/003306_54497daa25b3fc239bca000d66b06239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F003306_54497daa25b3fc239bca000d66b06239.jpg&h=2318233d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗呢三個已經算係韓國健身圈子最出名果幾個<br />\n而且你搵搵下仲有好多<br />\n好多都唔差 不過肉量唔夠歐美body building咁恐怖<br />\n點解韓國健身既程度好香港咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同身邊朋友講做gym個個都係做幾次無咩成果就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccdf8cdfe8ff9579dd8bd6c9e132e1fbee1d5f4","tid":319311,"uid":89949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"答單一問，健身新手自己一個做，經常做到無力又做唔晒一set ，事後肌肉無咩feel，有無解救？"},{"pid":"605a0106c91a5768b1eac5b410bfe738f074a3a1","tid":319311,"uid":5014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答單一問，健身新手自己一個做，經常做到無力又做唔晒一set ，事後肌肉無咩feel，有無解救？</blockquote><br />\n唔夠力就玩輕啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d33dfda5a80ae3a4ba65c7fd73a5bf444e30d9","tid":319311,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"因為港女鐘意瘦仔多過肌肉男囉"},{"pid":"8110801f2bb50719ff7408bf8f8a3c7d760555aa","tid":319311,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答單一問，健身新手自己一個做，經常做到無力又做唔晒一set ，事後肌肉無咩feel，有無解救？</blockquote><br />\n拎一個自己覺得適合既重量<br />\n慢上慢落咁做<br />\n最緊要係食感覺 新手做得重無意思<br />\n慢慢加上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d651e117465d2ca819e0d28ec010de271efce7e9","tid":319311,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為港女鐘意瘦仔多過肌肉男囉</blockquote><br />\n相信大部份港女都係鍾意穿衣顯瘦脫衣有肉"},{"pid":"1527d76534547dbc9163842846e806d3adae9ec4","tid":319311,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:58:37.000Z","msg":"人哋又服兵役又練跆拳..."},{"pid":"4d6c247ec3b330e09ffbe439dae1b3b570c1f28b","tid":319311,"uid":103593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係架啦，人哋重視外表呀嘛"},{"pid":"25291fbe64e242e8d066bcc68040d43b288ece1a","tid":319311,"uid":44525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為港女鐘意瘦仔多過肌肉男囉</blockquote><br />\n我見好多港女拖條仔係好瘦<br />\n對雞瘦到香雞腳咁"},{"pid":"176b07b25bb42354a3046355e887bf0a66e9c217","tid":319311,"uid":62830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港啲人要追夢打機呀嘛"},{"pid":"9437a05da26d54bfb5475983a05457a3f65fe40a","tid":319311,"uid":89949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"多謝真心解答。"},{"pid":"b68964973b8be0630f61473c968c0448763350b7","tid":319311,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"個個都做先唔正常<br />\n<br />\n有興趣咪自己去做飽佢<br />\n<br />\n純粹健康既<br />\n跑步/踩單車 好多帶氧都做到<br />\n<br />\n健身都係外觀原因推動多過健康因素"},{"pid":"c79d3daaa1a58f956d752c9995210e0a2caf58f0","tid":319311,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"樓主有心嘅就keep住做啦<br />\n等同溝女投資咋嘛，依d野要放長線架<br />\n何況每次做完都好有滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間嘅又有益嘅<br />\n點解唔去做吓而走咗去玩呢<br />\n利申唔鍾意d人睇戲睇人相，得把口講羨慕但又唔去做（尢其是d香港男仔）"},{"pid":"12c8730b826d7ade216c9aae96f65af6c3e1fa03","tid":319311,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:24:20.000Z","msg":"韓國佬差唔多個個都用藥咁款"},{"pid":"717233b96c31c0384a1acf33023fb51b88cc9557","tid":319311,"uid":64677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"香港人太忙,健身室又細又多sales煩鳩住,<br />\n加上好多人認為舉一舉就會變大隻呢種觀念<br />\n<br />\n利申:返工返9點,朝早去完gym先返工"},{"pid":"89f4465e68e568b52a484e47e7a05ff4c018424e","tid":319311,"uid":12102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人太忙,健身室又細又多sales煩鳩住,<br />\n加上好多人認為舉一舉就會變大隻呢種觀念<br />\n<br />\n利申:返工返9點,朝早去完gym先返工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"fc9f53246cc12c4cd20e583c610f55349d59fce6","tid":319311,"uid":59078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"想掩蓋鳩細既事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f64b6d98ae5466f7a183a6369b8abec82886d7","tid":319311,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人太忙,健身室又細又多sales煩鳩住,<br />\n加上好多人認為舉一舉就會變大隻呢種觀念<br />\n<br />\n利申:返工返9點,朝早去完gym先返工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：朝朝六點起身做gym"},{"pid":"a7a5b98cdea0154b00bd5c1f884c98ed37b673a5","tid":319311,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"點解韓仔啲肌肉咁怪 好完美咁一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973f978694206b6215e99e4bcb2c1ba5a2be5c52","tid":319311,"uid":88260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解韓仔啲肌肉咁怪 好完美咁一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有食藥"},{"pid":"3778afd1f8e298a41d5c2d4bfb95aeaf5376b700","tid":319311,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解韓仔啲肌肉咁怪 好完美咁一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有食藥</blockquote><br />\n食藥or打針既肌肉樣好似唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地似收得好乾加影相效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左6年gym"},{"pid":"146cf09f36d0f716f6f747bfb75cc0161ca2ab8b","tid":319311,"uid":98836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都做先唔正常<br />\n<br />\n有興趣咪自己去做飽佢<br />\n<br />\n純粹健康既<br />\n跑步/踩單車 好多帶氧都做到<br />\n<br />\n健身都係外觀原因推動多過健康因素</blockquote><br />\n根本因為做gym商業價值大<br />\n先係咁推健身風氣 捧啲大隻佬上神枱<br />\n好似之前女人瘦身咁<br />\n要健康大把運動都得啦"},{"pid":"0d4b1d227495441fe4d253e061ab1d468cf96bb6","tid":319311,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解韓仔啲肌肉咁怪 好完美咁一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有食藥</blockquote><br />\n食藥or打針既肌肉樣好似唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地似收得好乾加影相效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左6年gym</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係因為皮膚好 同鬼佬硬係有啲唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91058207f7728d821ed63f723f9c335b4a3d4d35","tid":319311,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T22:17:24.000Z","msg":"你估人地服兵役流架<br />\n<br />\n你班港仔邊可能6點起身gym<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：5點半起身。7點搭正入場gym"},{"pid":"be6dc7d085ddc66e6be30714623719d6e962dd81","tid":319311,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解韓仔啲肌肉咁怪 好完美咁一舊一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有食藥</blockquote><br />\n食藥or打針既肌肉樣好似唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地似收得好乾加影相效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左6年gym</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係因為皮膚好 同鬼佬硬係有啲唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬼佬好多都無收乾依幾條友似為左影相先收乾身"}]}